RecBoot For Mac 2.1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADDED
- If device isn't in recovery mode and the user hits Exit Recovery, we don't send the usb commands anymore.
- When the user hits the close button, kills the application. Same as CMD+Q.
- Ohhai auto-updating system. - Sparkle
- 10.5.x support.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGED
- If the device is in a unknown mode or it is an unknown device, we now display this neatly in deviceString.
